{ Our move remains most natural and straightforward. We grab the center at the first chance. }
3... cxd4
{ 3...d5  4.exd5  Qxd5  will transpose to @@StartFEN@@rnbqkbnr/pp1ppppp/8/2p5/4P3/2P5/PP1P1PPP/RNBQKBNR b KQkq - 0 2@@EndFEN@@  2...d5  3.exd5  Qxd5  4.d4  g6  which we will examine thoroughlyhere. }
