{ The queen won't be safe on a5 as White will go after it later with a3-b4. }
9. a3
{ We are not hiding our intentions. Keeping b4 ideas in mind, and also to make sure when we play Bd3 Black won't have Nb4. }
9... Be7 { 9...Nd5  10.Bd2  doesn't improve the lifestyle of the queen on a5. }
10. Bd3
{ The bishop is nicely placed on d3, and White is ready to castle next. } 10...
O-O 11. O-O
