10. Nb5
{ This is an improvement over Jorden van Foreest his game, given by Sebastian in his Chessable course. }
10... Bb8 11. Bc5 Qxd1+ 12. Rxd1 Ne4 13. Ba3 a6 14. Nbd4
{ Here the variation stopped giving White a slight edge. } 14... Bd7
{ Black is ready to meet Nxc6 with Bxc6. } 15. Bd3 Nf6
