{ There are two sensible moves at this point. Black can retreat with his queen on d7 or d8.   8...Bd6  loses to a nice trick  9.Bc4  Qxc4  10.Nxd6+  with a fork.   By the number of games,  8...Qd8  is more popular, but  8...Qd7  is more trendy. }
