{ Black skips Nc6 and plans to solve his issue with the c8 bishop first.   9...Nc6  transposes to the line we will examinehere after @@StartFEN@@rnbqkb1r/pp3ppp/3pp3/3nP3/2BP4/5N2/PP3PPP/RNBQK2R b KQkq - 1 7@@EndFEN@@  7...Nc6 }
