{ After  19...axb6  20.gxf3  fxg5  21.Rc7  Ke8  22.Rfc1  nothing moves for Black while White threatens Rxb7-Rc8, and Black's only sensible option might be to stop the clock. }
20. d7
{ Without this brilliant deflecting move, the entire combination would not work.   It is very easy for our opponents to miss this move from a distance while playing 14... Qb6. }
