{ Black needs one move to enjoy his material advantage. } 22. Rc7
{ Another super crucial move. We must force Black to go back to e8. } 22... Ke8
23. Rd1
{ We are not giving Black time to consolidate. We will wipe out the queenside while Black cannot develop the kingside and the rook on h8 is helpless. }
