13... Nd5
{ Another very tempting move. Black wants to plant his knight on f4. } 14. Nxc4
{ It is fantastic to see how engines are calm about Black's attack on the kingside. }
14... Nf4 { Hard to imagine any other move for Black. } 15. Qf1
{ The only move, but it's not rocket science!   Not to lose immediately, Black must find an incredible imaginary and risky-looking move. }
15... b5
